name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: ( CASE WHEN FIND_IN_SET( #{srf.sessioncontext.srfloginname}, t1.collector ) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: ISFAVOURITES

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: (select count(1) from zt_module t where t.deleted = '0' and t.type = 'doc' and t.parent = 0 and t.root = t1.id)
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: MODULECNT

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: (select t.date from zt_action t where t.objectID = t1.id and t.objectType = 'doclib' and t.action = 'created')
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: OPENEDDATE

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`ACL`,
t1.`CREATEBY`,
t1.`DELETED`,
t1.`DEPTNAME`,
t1.`DOCLIBSN`,
'doc' AS `DOCLIBTYPE`,
t1.`GROUPS`,
t1.`ID`,
( CASE WHEN FIND_IN_SET( #{srf.sessioncontext.srfloginname}, t1.collector ) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS `ISFAVOURITES`,
t1.`MAIN`,
t1.`MDEPTID`,
(select count(1) from zt_module t where t.deleted = '0' and t.type = 'doc' and t.parent = 0 and t.root = t1.id) AS `MODULECNT`,
t1.`NAME`,
(select t.date from zt_action t where t.objectID = t1.id and t.objectType = 'doclib' and t.action = 'created') AS `OPENEDDATE`,
t1.`ORDER`,
t1.`ORGID`,
t1.`ORGNAME`,
t1.`PRODUCT`,
t11.`name` AS `PRODUCTNAME`,
t1.`PROJECT`,
t21.`NAME` AS `PROJECTNAME`,
t1.`TYPE`,
t1.`UPDATEBY`,
t1.`UPDATEMANNAME`
FROM `zt_doclib` t1 
LEFT JOIN `zt_product` t11 ON t1.`PRODUCT` = t11.`id` 
LEFT JOIN `zt_project` t21 ON t1.`PROJECT` = t21.`ID`
